<div class="hero-image-container">
  <%= image_tag("dpi_building.jpeg", class:"hero-image object-fit-cover", alt:"DPI Building") %>
  <div class="hero-text">
    <%# a bit odd to have a h7 before a h1 tag %>
    <h7>Pritzker Tech Talent Labs /</h7>
    <h1>Full-Stack Developer Apprentice Mentorships</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="blue-background">
  <div class="container blue-background-text">
    <h4>A Core Part of The Software Development Apprenticeship Program</h4>
    <hr>
    <p>DPIâ€™s Full Stack Software Development Apprenticeship Program works with corporations to identify and train tech talent in both technical skills and soft skills to fill critical roles in the Chicagoland area. 
    Mentorship plays a vital role in improving these skills and helping a trainee grow personally and professionally.</p>
    <h5 class="mt-5 mb-3">Interested in joining as a mentor or mentee?</h5>
    <%= link_to "Sign Up Now", new_user_registration_path, class:"btn btn-success btn-lg" %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-body-secondary py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h3 class="text-center mb-5">Through 1-on-1 mentoring, trainees will: </h3>
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3">
      <div class="col mb-3">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column card to-be-replaced text-white align-items-center py-4 px-4">
          <h5 class="card-title text-center"><strong>Gain New Perspective</strong></h5>
          <ul class="px-4">
            <li class="my-2">Hear from experiences of working professionals and what is important in real-life scenarios</li>
            <li class="my-2">Receive industry insights and advice in navigating through challenging situations</li>
            <li class="my-2">Challenge existing assumptions and viewpoints and foster critical thinking.</li>
          </ul>
          <p><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass fa-2xl text-success"></i></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col mb-3">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column card to-be-replaced text-white align-items-center py-4 px-4">
          <h5 class="card-title text-center"><strong>Develop Skills</strong></h5>
          <ul class="px-4">
            <li class="my-2">Refine skills for effective communication, both verbal and nonverbal</li>
            <li class="my-2">Practice networking, fostering stronger interpersonal connections, and navigating social dynamics </li>
            <li class="my-2">Discuss relevant tech stacks and the best ways to apply them</li>
          </ul>
          <p><i class="fa-solid fa-comments fa-2xl text-success"></i></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col mb-3">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column card to-be-replaced text-white align-items-center py-4 px-4">
          <h5 class="card-title text-center"><strong>Receive Personal Feedback</strong></h5>
          <ul class="px-4">
            <li class="my-2">Absorb constructive criticisms on portfolio, LinkedIn profile, self-introductions, etc.</li>
            <li class="my-2">Evaluate self-confidence, assertiveness, and self-advocacy skills, and use them to develop a strong personal branding</li>
            <li class="my-2">Try out different styles of interpersonal interactions and delivery of your story</li>
          </ul>
          <p><i class="fa-solid fa-file-pen fa-2xl text-success"></i></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="blue-background">
  <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-center align-items-center gap-4">
    <div class="bg-body-secondary card to-be-replaced py-4 px-4">
      <h5 class="card-title text-center">How does it work?</h5>
      <p>As a mentor:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Join a program as a mentor</li>
        <li>Specify how many mentees you can take on</li>
        <li>View mentee profiles</li>
      </ul>
      <p>As a mentee:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Join a program as a mentee</li>
        <li>View mentor profiles</li>
        <li>List up to 5 mentors in order of your preference to match</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
    <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
      <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/96-tfpSgK1c?si=BdMFuyVHahEGSgWv"  allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
